    </div>   
 </div>
 <div>

<h2>What bike do you ride?</h2>
<p>A bright blue Raleigh Solitaire - not ideal for longer journeys but I love it.</p>
<h2>What helped you to cycle in London?</h2>
<p>The fact that you at least have the idea you are contributing to a greener city, while saving money and getting some exercise.</p>
<h2>What has helped you get more out of riding a bike?
</h2>
<p>I once attended a meeting from the <a href="http://camdencyclists.org.uk/">Camden Cycling Campaign</a>, which was interesting and insightful as it was a platform for sharing ideas to improve the cycling landscape in London.</p>
